text: Ol i save senis long 'quarter' i go long 'half mile run', long dispela taim spit em i no impoten na pasin bilong stap strong na go het yet em i impoten.
Lukluk long wanem ol raun ol 'agent' i wok long mekim promosen long en, maski em long wanpela websait o long wanpela windua bilong stoa.
Populesen (population) bilong Vatican City em i kain olsem 800. Dispela em nambawan liklik kantri tru insait long wol na kantri we i gat liklik populesen tru.
'Experiment' bilong Hershey and Chase em i wanpela bilong ol samting we i tok olsem DNA em i wanpela 'genetic material'.
Ol Cook Islands em ol wanpela ailan kantri long we i save wok bung wantaim New Zealand, na em i stap long Polynesa, long namel bilong South Pacific Ocean.
Sapos yu laik lainim long tromoi wanpela 'boomerang' we i kam bek long han bilong yu, yu mas sekim na lukim olsem yu gat wanpela gutpela 'boomerang' we i ken tanim i kam bek.
'Downhill skiing' olsem wanpela 'sport' em i go bek long kain olsem '17th century' o moa, na long 1861 ol Norwegians i opim namba wan 'recreational ski club' long Australia.
Em i wanpela bilong ol bikpela samting we i save pulim ol turis i go long South Africa na ol i save lukim em olsem impoten samting insait long South African National Parks (SANParks).
Planti taim ol i save yusim ol narapela kain komputa long rekodim musik bai em i ken proesesim (process) na miksim ol saun wantaim.
Eksampel em, yumi i ken tok olsem kar i mekim na ol manmeri i kamapim ol rot.
Ol i yusim ol 'dump truck' long blokim ol maus bilong ol tanel (tunnel ) we i go insait na 80-pela polis manmeri i helpim ol long salim ol ol kar i go long ol narapela rot.
Dr. Tony Moll i painimaut long dispela Extremely Drug Resistant Tuberculosis (XDR-TB) long KwaZulu-Natal rijen bilong South Africa.
General James Ewing bai kisim 700 lain bilong pait na brukim wara long Trenton Ferry, na holimpasim bris i stap antap long Assunpink Creek na banisim ol soldia bilong birua long ranawe.
Dispela hap tok 'safari' we planti lain i save yusim em i toktok long travel long graun long lukim ol narakain animal bilong Africa, planti bilong ol em ol animal bilong 'savanna'.
MetroRail i gat tupela level long ol trein bilong i go i kam long wok na raun long Cape Town: MetroPlus (em ol i save kolim olsem First Class) na Metro (ol i save kolim Third Class).
Dispela hap tok 'cell' em i kam long tok ples Latin 'cella' we i min olsem wanpela liklik rum.
Nervous System i save mentenim 'homeostasis' taim em i salim ol 'nerve impulses' i go long olgeta hap bilong bodi na mekim blut i ron na tu, em i mekim blut i go gut long olgeta hap bilong bodi.
Ol 'alloy'em ol samting we i gat tupela o moa metel (metal) insait long en. No ken lus tingting olsem i gat planti elemen (element) insait long 'periodic table'.
Dispela 'show' em pastaim em ol 'voice actor' we i no gat planti save na ekspiriens (experience) i ektim, na ol i bilong East Texas.
Long wanpela intaviu, em i tok olsem dispela nupela 'variant' i bin "kamapim bikpela hevi na pret bikos long planti manmeri i dai."
34 pesen (percent) bilong ol lain insait long dispela 'poll' i gat dispela tingting, we ol i laik olsem Queen Elizabeth II i mas kamap laspela kwin bilong Australia.
'Day hiking' em i gat ol mak bilong wokabaut we i aninit long wanpela 'mile' na i go inap long mak bilong wokabaut we wanpela i ken mekim long wanpela de.

Ol 'downhill snowsport', we i gat 'skiing' na 'snowboarding', em ol 'sport' we planti lain i save long en na yu bai slaid (slide) i go daun long wanpela hap wantaim 'skis' o 'snowboard' we ol i pasim long lek bilong yu.
Long infomesen i kam long dispela fosil (fossil), em i min olsem dispela 'split' i kamap bipo long taim we planti savemanmeri i tingim bikos long 'molecular evidence'.
Sapos yu go raun na lukim Greenland long taim bilong kol em i impoten olsem yu mas kisim kol klos, (tingim taim yu go moa long hap not, ples bai i kol moa).
Isipela we bilong statim bisnis bilong 'travel writing' em long stretim pasin bilong yu long rait taim yu statim wanpela 'travel blog' websait.

Tru tru, ol 'region codes' i no senisim wanpela samting long pasin bilong brukim lo na mekim kopi; wanapela ' bit-for-bit' kopi i ken pilai gut long wanpela divai (device) wankain olsem 'original' kopi.
Dispela sik em ol pik i save karim, na ol moskito i save kisim long pik na givim i go long ol manmeri.
Ol i luk olsem ol rum. Em i namba wan man long lukim ol 'cell' we i dai pinis.

Dispela siti bilong Beijing long China em bai kamap olsem 'host city' bilong Olympic Winter Games long 2022, dispela bai i mekim em i kamap olsem namba wan siti bilong kamap 'host' bilong winta (winter) na sama (summer) Olympics.
Oyapock River Bridge em i wanpelad 'cable-stayed bridge'. Em i stap long Oyapock River na konektim ol siti bilong Oiapoque insait long Brazil na Saint-Georges de l'Oyapock insait long French Guiana.
Planti manmeri i save makim ples bilong ol bipo yet (bikos ol bot i save pulap long taim we planti manmeri i save laikim).
Ol 'hostel' em i bilong ol yanpela manmeri – wanpela 'guest' bilong en em bai stap long mak bilong ol twentipela krismas – tasol yu ken painim ol olpela travela tu i stap long hap.
Planti bilong ol dispela tempel i gat wanpela Annual bikde we i stat long Novemba na i pinis long Mid of May, we i save senis senis bihain kalenda bilong wanwan tempel long olgeta yia.
Sampela saintis i ting olsem ol Triceratop i bin kaikai ol 'cycad', wanpela kain plent (plant) we i save gro long planti hap long Cretaceous.

Long 11:20, ol polis i askim ol lain i mekim protes long surik i go bek long sait bilong rot, ol i tok olsem ol i nid long larim ol lain i protes bilong em i 'right' bilong ol na ol i nid long larim kar i go i kam long rot tu.
Ol narapela 'skiing events' bai kamap long Taizicheng ski eria long Zhangjiakou, kain olsem 220 km (140 'miles') long Beijing.
Husat lain i mekim plen long go long wanpela kantri we woa i save kamap lng en i mas kisim treining (training) i kam long ol profesenol.

Dispela 'unmanned lunar orbiter' Chandrayaan-1 i rausim Moon Impact Probe (MIP) bilong em, na dispela i flai antap long Moon long 1.5 kilomita long wanpela sekon (3000 'mile' long wanpela aua), na i 'crash land' gut klostu long 'south pole' bilong Moon.
Na tu, long ol ples we i hot ol bekteria (bacteria) i ken gro hariap moa na stap longpela taim autsait long bodi.
Wanwan taim i save i gat balus i go long insait bilong Antarctica long ol lain bilong klaimim maunten o bilong i go long Pole. I gat bikpela 'base' i stap long Pole.
Dispela 'algae' i save kamapim wanpela 'neurotoxin' we i ken mekim 'nerve' insait long ol manmeri na ol pis long i no wok.

Three Kingdoms em i wanpela bilong ol taim bilong pait insait long histori bilong Ancient China we planti tausen manmeri i dai taim ol pait long sindaun long nambawan sia insait long 'grand palace' long Xi’an.
Sapos yu go sua long sait bilong wara wantaim ol 'shipboard excursion' yu bai no gat nid long i gat wanpela narapela visa (dispela em i stat long 2009).
Dispela wok painimaut i givim sampela tingting tu long wanem we gras bilong pisin i save kamap.
I luk olsem sampela bilong ol sikmanmeri i bin kisim dispela binatang long haus sik, Dr, Moll i ting olsem, na tupela bilong ol lain em ol wokmanmeri bilong haus sik.
Taim yu bin i go long narapela kantri long namba wan taim tru, yu bin isi na traim long lainim samting, yu save olsem ol travela i stap long narapela kantri i mas senisim tingting na pasin bilong ol.
Pasin bilong sekuriti long sekim ol manmeri long ol 'checkpoint' i wok long kamap nogut moa bihain long Septemba 11, 2001.
Nau ol manmeri i save raitim ol tok save long ol komputa skrin (computer screen), na ol i no kam klostu long wanpela sapena (sharpener).

Ol lain i go pas long dispela wok painimaut i ting olsem, maski dispela em i tel bilong wanpela yangpela dainaso, dispela i soim olsem gras bilong pisin i stap long ol bikpela dainaso i no planti olsem gras bilong pikinini dainaso.
Mak bilong Hydrogen (dispela H insait long pH) 'ion' insait long kemikel (chemical) we ol i testim bai soim level bilong pH.
Tasol, taim yu mekim wanpela DVD, bai yu katim ol sait sait bilong em tu, na sapos vidio i gat ol toktok we ol i raitim klostu tumas long daunbilo, ol dispela toktok bai i no inap long kamap.
I no gat ripot bilong longpela 'traffic delay' long 'bletway', dispela narapela rot bilong go long siti.
Aninit long ol em ol namel sais pusi we i save kaikai ol namel sais abus stat long rebit (rabbit) i go long entelop (antelope) na dia (deer).

Dispela 'strain' bilong 'bird flu' em i nogut tru long ol manmeri, H5N1, na ol savemanmeri i tokaut olsem trutru dispela sik i go long wanpela wail pato na em i dai, na ol i painim em long Mande, long ol ples tais klostu long Lyon long hap is bilong France.

Ol i yusim ol 'crossties' pastaim long holim ol dispela 'track' i stap long wanpela ples. Bihain, nau, ol i luksave olsem ol dispela 'track' bai kamap gutpela moa sapos ol i gat wanpela hap ain i stap antap long ol.
Ol nambawan samting we i soim olsem 'internal poisoning' i kamap em wanpela kontena bilong marasin o 'toxic chemical' bilong haus i op na i stap.
Dispela em i gutpela sans bilong lukim Aurora borealis, taim skai bai tudak long klostu olgeta aua long kilok.
'Area' bilong Turkey i mekim em i stap olsem namba 37 bikpela kantri, na sais bilong em i olsem sais bilong Metropolitan France na United Kingdom taim tupela i bung wantaim.
House Speaker bilong bipo Newt Gingrich, gavana bilong Texas Rick Perry, na Congresswoman Michele Bachmann i pinis namba foa, faiv na siks.
Dispela grup ailan i stap 120 km not long Peninsula. Nambawan bikpela ailan em King George Island we i gat ol man i stap long Villa Las Estrellas.
U.S President George W. Bush i welkamim dispela tok save.
I gat kainkain senis i ken kamap, tasol dispela em i ol samting we planti manmeri i save mekim taim ol tok olsem ol "i go long Disney World".

Namba wan as tingting bilong Italy em long kisim ol kantri long Africa. Long holimpasim ol dispela kantri, ol i mas i gat hap bilong salim ol man bilong pait, olsem na ol man bilong pait bai i sel long Mediterranean Sea na kisim Africa.
South Africa em i nambawan tim insait long dispela tonamen (tournament) na em i stat gut taim em i winim tim bilong Zambia we i stap namba 5 insait long tonamen 26 - 00.
Insait long wanpela karis, ol i ron i go bek long Paris taim ol bikpela lain manmeri i belhat na i raunim ol na i wok long singaut na mekim ol kainkain toktok bilong pretim King na Queen.
Man we i winim silva medel (silver medal) long 2004 Olympic i tok, "Tru tru mi ting olsem ol meri i mas no ken pait. Dispela em i tingting bilong mi."
Beijing bai hostim (host) 'opening' na 'closing' seremoni na ol 'indoor ice events'.
Dispela tingting i go agensim narapela tingting we i tok olsem i no gat 'geological activity' i save kamap long mun.
I gat ol planti kainkain konstraksen bilong ol ai, we i bihainim wanwan samting i stap insait long wanpela animal o bihainim wanem samting dispela animal i nidim.
Schengen zone, em i narakain, sampela taim em i save stap olsem wanpela kantri bilong em yet.
Insait long 1960, Brezezinski i wok olsem wanpela edvaisa bilong John F. Kennedy na bihain em i wok long Lyndon B. Johnson edministresen.
Long 1957 Luxembourge i kamap olsem wanpela memba we i kamapim dispela oganaisesen we tude yumi save long em olsem European Union.
Dispela stori em ol i soim long 'opera' bilong France, we Camille Saint-Saens i raitim, em i stori bilong 'artist' "we laip bilong em i bihainim laikim bilong em long ol drag (drug) na Japan."

Bihain long ol samting i no kamap gut long ol soldia, Ethelred i wanbel long wanem ol samting Olaf i tok long en, na Olaf i go bek long Norway long traim na kisim bek kingdom bilong em. Em i winim sampela samting, tasol sampela samting i no kamap gut long em.
Na bihain ol i salim em i go long Addenbrooke's Hospital long Cambridge.
Long taim bilong turis long i go raun long ol stesin i stap long maunten i save kamap long bikpela mak tru long sama (summer) taim bilong India.
Ol narapela em Livingston Island, na Deception we 'flooded caldera' bilong volkeno we i ektif (active) yet i save givim wanpela kain lukluk bilong dispela basis.

Narapela resis bilong em, Giant Slalom, em i pinis namba ten insait long 'women's siiting group' wantaim ran taim bilong 4:41.30, 2:11.60 minit bihain long meri i kam long namba wan ples Austrian Claudia Loesch na 1:09.02 bihain long meri i kam long namba nain ples Gyöngyi Dani bilong Hungary.
Murray i lusim namba wan 'set' bilong em insait long wanpela 'tie breal' taim tupela man wantaim i kisim olgeta 'serve' insait long dispela 'set'.
'Pyramid sound and light show' em i wanpela samting we ol pikinini i save laikim na em i stap long dispela eria.
Maski 'immigration check' em i no save stap o i no save kamap taim yu kam bek long kantri bilong yu, 'customs control' em i ken hat wok liklik.
Taim yu stap tasol long haus na holide, yu gat taim long mekim yu yet amamas na kisim sampela taim long mekim wanpela naispela ti o kofi.
Sampela 'atom' i gat 'unstable nuclei' na dispela em i min olsem ol i save bruk taim yu tasim liklik o i no tasim.
Long Sande, Presiden bilong United States Donald Trump, i tok insait long wanpela leta we press secretary bilong em i ritim, em i tok olsem ol soldia bilong US bai i lusim kantri Syria.
Dispela 'satellite' long 'space' i kisim dispela kol (call) na salim em i kam daun bek gen, wantu tru.
Wanpela narapela man long Greek we planti lain i save long en em Pythagoras, planti lain i save long em bikos long 'theorem' bilong em long ol sait bilong ol 'right triangles'.
Ol sampela manmeri i ting olsem em i tok stret, tasol planti manmeri i bilim long oposit (opposite); ol i bilip olsem Solar System i save muv raunim Earth, wantaim Sun (na ol narapela sta tu).
Ol 'casino' i save traim hat tru long yusim taim na mani we ol 'guest' i kam na spendim. I no gat windua na klok, na ol dua bilong go autsait em i save hat long painim.
Long ol liklik ailan na ol raunwara, yu bai no inap nidim wanpela 'yatch'.
Long sama (summer), yu bai nid long lukaut long ol natnat sapos yu tingting long wokabaut i go insait long renfores (rainforest).
Dispela muvi we Ryan Gosling na Emma Stone i stap insait long en, em ol lain i makim em long i stap insait long olgeta bikpela 'category'.
Yu bai no inap westim taim bilong yu long wokabaut hap aua i go long dispela liklik ples we i gat ol narapela kain samting.
Ol sta i save givim lait na hot bikos long eneji (enegry) we i kamap taim ol 'hydrogen atom' i pas (o 'fuse') wantaim long kamap ol narapela 'element' we i hevi moa.
Long 1995 ol i votim (vote) em olsem nambawan pleiya (player) insait long histori bilong Partizan.
'Sleep interruption' em i pasin bilong kirap namel long slip na go bek long slip sotpela taim bihain (10–60 minit).
Tude ol i save yusim ol komputa long senisim ol piksa na vidio.
Insait long Rogaland na Agdar ol i save kolim "‘hei’" na em i min olsem wanpela gras ples we i no gat diwai na ‘heather’ i save karamapim.

Long ol 'extreme' bilong dispela 'poll', 29 pesen (percent) bilong ol dispela sevei (survey) i bilip olsem Australia i mas kamap wanpela 'republic' hariap, taim 31 pesen i bilip olsem Australia i mas no ken kamap wanpela 'republic'.
